<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>Hello MUI</title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/mui.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">

		<style type="text/css">
			.mui-content {
				background: none;
			}
			
			h2 {
				padding: 80px 0 10px;
				width: 140px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				position: relative;
			}
			
			h2 img {
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: auto;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			
			h2 p {
				font-size: 16px;
				color: #666;
				line-height: 22px;
				width: 166px;
				height: 120px;
				background: url(../../img/medication/bg_talk.png) no-repeat scroll top left;
				background-size: 85% 60%;
				position: absolute;
				left: -70px;
				top: 28px;
				padding: 20px 0 0 15px;
			}
			
			.medicationSave a {
				width: 260px;
				margin: 25px auto;
				border-radius: 8px;
				color: #fff;
			}
			
			.meFamily-tip {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 16px;
				color: #2a2a2a;
				padding: 10px 0;
			}
			
			article {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #4A4A4A;
				margin-top: -20px;
			}
			
			article span {
				color: red;
				opacity: .6;
			}
			
			article div {
				padding-top: 20px;
				width: 260px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				border: 1px solid #C0C0C0;
				border-radius: 10px;
			}
			
			article h2 {
				position: relative;
				bottom: -15px;
				background: #F2F6F9;
				padding-top: 0;
				width: 200px;
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #4A4A4A;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<header class="mui-bar mui-bar-nav">
			<a class="mui-icon mui-icon-left-nav mui-pull-left" id="indexFamilyDoctorBackId"></a>
			<h1 class="mui-title">我的家人</h1>
			<!--			<a href="" class="btn-add mui-pull-right" id="addFamily" style="font-size:14px;line-height: 40px;" id="addFamily">新增</a>-->
		</header>
		<div class="mui-content">
			<h2>
				<p>您还没添加家人</p>
				<img src="../../img/medication/icon_yongyaozhushou.png"/>
			</h2>
			<p class="meFamily-tip">
				添加家人，随时随地关爱家人健康
			</p>
			<article>
				<h2>有了健医宝,您可以为家人</h2>
				<div>
					<p> <span>建立健康档案</span>,时时备查</p>
					<p><span>记录血糖血压</span>,管理健康</p>
					<p><span>设定用药方案</span>,温馨提示</p>
				</div>
			</article>
			<div class="medicationSave">
				<a class="mui-btn mui-btn-block addFamily" href="">添加家人</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script src="../../js/juicer-min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
	<script src="../../js/mui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/core/config.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/core/common.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/route.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		//绑定回退事件
		document.getElementById("indexFamilyDoctorBackId").addEventListener("tap", function() {
			var mianPage = plus.webview.getLaunchWebview();
			mui.openWindow({
				id: mianPage.id,
				url: mianPage.uri,
				extras: {
					index: 4
				}
			});
		});
	</script>

</html>